{{Path|/etc/portage/color.map}} is a file containing variables that define color classes used by Portage. Portage will check this file first for color class settings. If no color class has been set in {{Path|/etc/portage/color.map}}, Portage uses default values defined internally.

== Format ==

* Variable = [space delimited list of attributes or ANSI code pattern]
* Attribute = [space delimited list of colors (see below) or ANSI code pattern]

